played in our mortal flesh. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 10:21","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":21},{"label":"Jn 8:51","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":51},{"label":"Php 3:10","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:4:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So then, death is at work in us, but life in you. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:4:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And since we have the same spirit of faith in keeping with what is written, I believed, therefore I spoke,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 116:10","book":"Psa","chapter":116,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 116:10","book":"Psa","chapter":116,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" we also believe, and therefore speak. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 116:10","book":"Psa","chapter":116,"verse":10},{"label":"Ps 116:10","book":"Psa","chapter":116,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:4:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For we know that the one who raised the Lord Jesus will also raise us with Jesus "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 4:14","book":"1Th","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and present us with you. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Th 4:14","book":"1Th","chapter":4,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:4:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Indeed, everything is for your benefit so that, as grace extends through more and more people, it may cause thanksgiving "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 9:11","book":"2Co","chapter":9,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" to increase to the glory of God."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Co 9:11","book":"2Co","chapter":9,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:4:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore we do not give up. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 3:13","book":"2Th","chapter":3,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Even though our outer person is being destroyed, our inner person "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 7:22","book":"Rom","chapter":7,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" is being renewed day by day. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Th 3:13","book":"2Th","chapter":3,"verse":13},{"label":"Rm 7:22","book":"Rom","chapter":7,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:4:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For our momentary light affliction "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 6:2","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" is producing for us an absolutely incomparable eternal weight of glory. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 24:26","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:1","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:4","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gl 6:2","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":2},{"label":"Lk 24:26","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":26},{"label":"1Pt 5:1","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":1},{"label":"1Pt 5:4","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:4:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So we do not focus on what is seen, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:24","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" but on what is unseen. For what is seen is temporary, but what is unseen is eternal."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 8:24","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783099541677}